{"tid":1199939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"職安健網上投訴平台啟用　僱員可用手機向勞工處舉報","createTime":"2019-06-10T15:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:25:45.000Z","uid":206097,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10722eb62621c040c20dc65b7c02eac494231530","tid":1199939,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:31:07.000Z","msg":"香港建造業奪命工業意外頻生，為加強工人的職安健意識，勞工處今日(19日)推出網上職業安全及健康投訴平台，讓僱員及公眾人士透過流動電子裝置或電腦，更方便地就工作地點的不安全作業模式或環境狀況，以電子表格形式向勞工處作出舉報。處方強調，除在法例特定的情況下，勞工處不會披露投訴人的資料，亦不會披露因收到投訴而到訪某工作地點。<br />\n網上平台可讓投訴人更快捷及方便地就職安健不當作業作投訴，令勞工處能夠盡快跟進以防止意外發生。投訴人可以透過智能電話、平板電腦等流動電子裝置，到勞工處網頁： <a href=\"http://www.labour.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw1hCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=06b9bba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.labour.gov.hk</a> 填寫電子表格作出舉報，並可上傳相片、影片或錄音檔案。<br />\n勞工處收到投訴後，會因應投訴的性質及內容，盡快派員巡視相關的工作地點，作出針對性的調查及跟進，處方亦已適當地安排人手以配合這些調查跟進工作。<br />\n<br />\n唔止建造業可以舉報，飲食業同各個行業既同仁都可以到網上平台舉報不安全既作業模式同環境。"},{"pid":"c1d01ca8ae083e20b906dbd1c6a0bcf35af980b5","tid":1199939,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8e524d2a2db5dddfc7314bfb906159a8e6c31c","tid":1199939,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467cde57f01c3ad0814822f084d889140abe5a25","tid":1199939,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b17a1578242f750cbda02316243c4c236e109bb","tid":1199939,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T22:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693320642ed73880fe2bbbfad570586a934a005b","tid":1199939,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fabe0250e7b1b2d3c72fa56fc0e9366d810d7cc","tid":1199939,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}